  "name": "Eyes of Night",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/magic/perception/eye-ringed-glow-angry-teal.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 1st level, You can see through the deepest gloom. You have <strong>darkvision </strong>out to a range of <strong>300 feet</strong>. In that radius, you can see in dim light as if it were bright light and in darkness as if it were dim light.</p>\n<p>As an <strong>action</strong>, you can magically share the darkvision of this feature with willing creatures you can see within 10 feet of you, up to a number of creatures equal to your Wisdom modifier (minimum of one creature). The shared darkvision lasts for <strong>1 hour</strong>. Once you share it, you can't do so again until you finish a long rest, unless you expend a spell slot of any level to share it again.</p>",
